Based on John Steinbeck's novella, Of Mice and Men.

Disclaimer:

This is a rage game to represent the struggles of living during the Great Depression, however, it is a very joke-y interpretation of the harsh conditions.

Don't take what actually happens in the game seriously, just remember your struggles with this game are intentional and rage-quitting the game would be the same as rage-quitting life back then.

Also, please read John Steinbeck's Of Mice and Men before playing. This game doesn't provide enough story to be an actual summary of the book.
